{"ID":"20240127164901-sxq8s7v","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240127164901-sxq8s7v","title":"开篇","updated":"20240127164943"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-5499vde","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-5499vde","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前言"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-q1d48vv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-q1d48vv","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"VR行业发展是越来越火热了，硬件设备上有HTC VIVE，Oculus rift，PS VR，各种魔镜；平台上有Steam VR，Gear VR，Google Daydream。而游戏引擎上则有两大阵营：Unreal Engine和Unity。Unity凭着先期的移动平台优势占领了一大部分移动平台的市场，所以目前上手机上的VR游戏也大部分是由Unity开发的。而PC平台上，Unreal Engine凭借着优异的性能，绚丽的渲染效果，源码开源的战略也抢占了目前大部分PC平台VR游戏的份额。参加一场ChinaJoy的VR游戏，会发现大部分也都是由UE4开发的。虽然UE4的授权分成费确实比Unity要昂贵一些，但也因为VR行业本身也还处以社会主义初级阶段，大家也都是在做Demo性质的产品，还没有形成非常客观的市场利润市场。所以盈利后的那些分成费在现阶段已经不太有所谓了。"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-vs03g4x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-vs03g4x","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大名鼎鼎的的虚幻引擎，从1998开始，到我们知道的UE3,UDK，一直是高大上的3A游戏和端游的渲染器引擎。然后到2013年，UE4大刀阔斧的改革，干掉了UnrealScript，引进了Blueprint蓝图系统，直接让策划美术也可以拖线实现游戏逻辑。更大的改变的是竟然开源了，受益于社区的回馈，版本更新的速度更是丧心病狂。小版本更新几乎是一两个月就一版。在学习了Unity的Marketplace和插件系统后，更是如虎添翼，焕发了新的生命力。"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-8t3bglt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-8t3bglt","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽然官方一直非常努力的升级更新引擎，但UE4目前也存在了学习曲线陡峭，教程资源稀少的问题。笔者自己从事VR游戏开发，在学习UE4的过程中，基本上也只能硬啃官方文档，youtube上官方视频教程，还有一些寥寥的第三方的视频教程。而且更大的问题在于基本上所有的教程都是非常初级的，只是在教你怎么”用”这个引擎，所以一旦在使用过程中发现了问题，往往手足无措，不能高层建瓴的去解决问题。官方的文档虽然说已经挺详尽了，但大部分重点也只是在介绍表层的各种功能，对于引擎内部的结构和运作机理讳莫如深。如果把UE4当作Unity那样的一个黑盒子去用，在遇到Bug时也只能去各种试各种猜，那也无疑浪费了UE的一个大优势。"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-z1ehpcd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-z1ehpcd","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"UE4无疑是非常优秀的世界上最顶尖的引擎之一，性能和效果都非常出众，编辑器工作流也非常的出色，更难得宝贵的是完全的开源让我们有机会去从中吸取营养，学习世界上第一流游戏引擎的架构思想。"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-vhx55i3","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-vhx55i3","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240127164923-vbtd5sr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-vbtd5sr","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"源码面前，了无秘密 ——侯捷"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-lwq441r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-lwq441r","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以笔者决定开始该系列教程《Inside UE4》，从最最底层的C++源码剖析，到最最上层的蓝图节点，力求解释清楚各个选项的内部运作机理。希望做到知其然，而更要知其所以然。UE4也是一个非常博大精深的引擎，光源码下载下来也都有1~2G，分析透彻各个具体模块的运作机理无疑也是个艰巨的任务，但我们努力一分也至少有一分的收获，有一分的甜蜜。"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-4eyai9d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-4eyai9d","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"面向的读者："}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-d88pgib","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-d88pgib","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-f6x01a9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-f6x01a9","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-g2pxxbv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-g2pxxbv","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不满足于目前世面上教程深度的。已经大概知道了引擎功能并使用，但是仍然想要知道得更多的人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-nvi2nhm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-nvi2nhm","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-bnob4hv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-bnob4hv","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有一定的C++基础。UE4里的C++已经被Epic给魔改后又和C#厮混在一起，一方面得益于此，UE4里的C++实现了各种方便的功能，如反射，垃圾回收，编译系统等重量级的功能。一方面也加大了我们的阅读难度。所以需要你有良好的C++基础，至少看得懂各种C++模板，熟悉各种数据结构。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-kp9kemb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-kp9kemb","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-v6d06fw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-v6d06fw","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有一点点的C"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"tag","TextMarkTextContent":"语言能力，在涉及UE4编译系统的时候，会谈到一些C"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，还好不是很多，也还好C"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"tag","TextMarkTextContent":"作为一门非常优秀的语言非常易读，不过你要是已经掌握C"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，那就更好了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-73pfr52","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-73pfr52","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-vv04p7c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-vv04p7c","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"了解3D游戏引擎的一些基础概念，如知道什么是材质，什么是骨骼动画融合等。所幸这些都是很容易知道的知识。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-nrs6be3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-nrs6be3","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-ar7braa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-ar7braa","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有一些基本的图形学知识，知道Mesh,Shader,RenderTarget……等等一些基本的概念。本教程在开始某个专题的时候，会简单讲解一下背景知识，但它不会变成基础图形学教程。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-lbt4u2t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-lbt4u2t","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不适合的读者："}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-67uk3u4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-67uk3u4","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-xm2u9cp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-xm2u9cp","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-4n0ft5g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-4n0ft5g","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"希望通过该教程学习快速上手UE4引擎的人，不适合你。目前快速上手UE4的最佳途径依然是官方文档和视频教程。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-0a26pbk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-0a26pbk","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-q38m9cn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-q38m9cn","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"希望学习然后自己搭建具体游戏的，如FPS，VR游戏，样板间等。本系列教程不会教你从零开始搭建一个游戏示例，虽然会讲解VR的各种配置的内部机制原理。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-27g36xz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-27g36xz","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-7t2dk1h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-7t2dk1h","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"希望学习某个模块具体案例的，如用材质编辑器实现各种效果。本教程会透彻分析材质编辑器内部的实现机制，也会讲解各个材质节点的功能和原理，有时也会看需要通过一些非常直接简单的示例来讲解。但目标从来都是讲解原理，而不是实现结果。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-2o53qa2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-2o53qa2","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"愿景和计划"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-9cs5op4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-9cs5op4","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-dp5vpls","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-dp5vpls","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-yg7ht8z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-yg7ht8z","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从C++源码层次上分析整个游戏引擎的架构。了解清楚各个模块之间是怎么协作的，如果有闲情雅致，也甚至会具体到谈一谈某个很小的点为何这么设计。如UE4里的Delegate，Pointers，TArray等。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-3yt08pl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-3yt08pl","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-zsrvs4l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-zsrvs4l","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽然源码剖析本来就是曲线陡峭的上升，但还是希望能尽量深入浅出的讲解，所以也会尽量结合实际的效果演示。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-5r58xt8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-5r58xt8","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-4o2egou","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-4o2egou","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为UE4比较庞大，所以会逐渐的展开各个专题展开，在讲解一个专题的源码时，会暂时忽略其它跟它协作模块。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-qqersfd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-qqersfd","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-v5zw9tu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-v5zw9tu","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽然UE4也可以做移动平台的开发，但本教程还是主要专注于Windows的PC端游戏内容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-2hqey7l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-2hqey7l","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-ij4mpuk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-ij4mpuk","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"计划是连载周更，虽说已经有预定的专题讲解列表计划，但并不妨碍你留言告知你最想了解的下一个专题。我会酌情改变优先级。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-3rh7zo0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ni4=","Num":6},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-3rh7zo0","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-ppy5b6f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-ppy5b6f","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本人也是才疏学浅，经验有限，如有错误纰漏之处，也请不吝赐教，共同学习进步，不胜感激。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-3ylt5y3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-3ylt5y3","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一些准备工作"}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-mxystyi","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-mxystyi","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-2v2m9d5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-2v2m9d5","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-i3wpn8a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-i3wpn8a","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/EpicGames/UnrealEngine","TextMarkTextContent":"UnrealEngine官方Github地址"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n虽说官方已经提供了简便的launcher，但还是推荐自己自己Clone源码编译，也方便时不时的Debug和查看源码知道Why。而且有些时候其实是直接更改引擎源码来得更为方便便利的。\nClone下来之后先点 Setup.bat再点 GenerateProjectFiles.bat ，然后打开UE4.sln，按照默认选项DevelopmentEditor，等待最初半个小时的编译后，就可以开始源码之旅了。\n引擎版本紧跟Github最新release，目前最新4.14\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为UnrealEngine只是公开源码，但不是开源项目，依然是个私有项目。访问该Github地址，需要先链接你的Github到EpicGames的会员权限里，这个文档"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.unrealengine.com/ue4-on-github","TextMarkTextContent":"Linking your Github account"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说明了步骤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-koss6sd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-koss6sd","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-ooioq2n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-ooioq2n","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//docs.unrealengine.com/latest/INT/","TextMarkTextContent":"UnrealEngine官方文档"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n本教程也会同时大量引用官方文档的内容，在官方文档简略的介绍的基础上，通过源码加深理解，再更加透彻的解释。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-fvm295z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-fvm295z","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-ji4b4s6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-ji4b4s6","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/UnrealDevelopmentKit","TextMarkTextContent":"UnrealEngine官方Youtube频道"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-6ahbspn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-6ahbspn","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-qqja6fx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-qqja6fx","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//i.youku.com/i/UMzE2NDk2OTIw","TextMarkTextContent":"UnrealEngine官方优酷频道"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n有条件的话，还是建议自搭梯子，youtube的视频教程更新是最快的，而且也有高清。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-35sxzib","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-35sxzib","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240127164923-axu7oth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-axu7oth","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一块大容量的SSD，UE用source build的话，特别是想调试引擎的话，一个配置编译出来都得耗用个好几个G，一个项目的编译20~30G轻轻松松。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240127164923-95x8cks","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240127164923-95x8cks","updated":"20240127164923"},"Children":[{"Type